### Drill 8: Static Files & CORS

# Test Static file access
GET http://localhost:3000/static/index.html

###

# Test Manual CORS headers
GET http://localhost:3000/manual-cors

###

# Test Preflight (OPTIONS Request)
OPTIONS http://localhost:3000/manual-cors

###

# Test Global CORS Middleware (Open)
GET http://localhost:3000/open-cors

###

# Test Restricted CORS (Matching origin)
GET http://localhost:3000/restricted-cors
Origin: http://example.com

###

# Test Restricted CORS (Should block Origin header mismatch)
GET http://localhost:3000/restricted-cors
Origin: http://untrusted.com
